title: LF duo queue partners (high gold+, mid/jungle main)
body:
Ex plat 1 mid lf people to duo with, add RequieM 1

http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=RequieM+1

replies.body: i am midlane xerath main in high gold atm, i think i can reach plat but the easiest way would be to start duoing, (prior only solo) am looking for  a jungler duo who knows how to play around mid. ill send u a request in game and see if u r on. dunno if it works because maybe u rly like mid im mid/support and my xerath bot is exceptional
